  "description": "Repository and organization drilldown over curated GitHub Governance activity. v5 uses normalized audit-event inventory for Organization and Repository selectors and BigQuery-safe native Include All variables.",
  "editable": true,
  "fiscalYearStartMonth": 0,
  "graphTooltip": 0,
  "id": null,
  "links": [],
  "liveNow": false,
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "Repository Governance Activity",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 3,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0
      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "**Investigate curated governance activity for an organization or repository.**  \nScope: **${organization} / ${repository}** \u00b7 **${governance_area}** \u00b7 **${review_priority}** \u00b7 **${actor}**  \nThis is an event-history drilldown, not a current-state risk score."
